name: Enter Date in Date dropdown

testSteps.description: 1: Enter Date in Date dropdown ({parentTab=Leave Management, childTab=Apply, tab=Work From Home})

children.description: Given User is logged into MIS
When User is on MIS Home Page
When Click on "Apply" sub tab of "Leave Management" tab
Click on sub tab: Apply, Leave Management
Then Click on "Work From Home" Tab
Verify tab is active: Work From Home
Then Enter date in date dropdown
